    "I do not mind them basing suggestions of these things as I'm getting curated content.",
    "However, there should be an option for them to not automatically access such things as others may not be as liberal in this context….",
    "Another opinion was that explanations should be shown when the user gives permission.",
    "As pointed out in the interview, asking for users' consent of when and how to show information instills a feeling of active control over the system.",
    "According to one participant's opinions, it was evident that an explanation for recommendations can be conveyed whenever the users want, making the whole explainable recommendation system more controllable."
